Hi A-Team,

Sorry for not being in more communication this week. Hope the remainder of rehearsal as awesome!

Still making this show happen. Shoot and RSVP on here or email or call me if possible as well.

For those that haven been before we meet actually around the corner from harrison ave entrance at the women's housing, which from harrison is further back along the highway and next to the gas station.

Buzz me for questions or any other details.

We need to get there by 5:30 so we can do the show at 6pm.

Jason
